
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-chowdhury-netmip6-01.txt'>
    <title>"Network Based Layer 3 Connectivity and Mobility Management for IPv6", Kuntal  Chowdhury, Ajoy Singh</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-chowdhury-netmip6-01.txt</link>
    <description>The layer 3 connection and mobility management is essential in providing seamless access to services and enhanced user experience in a mobile and nomadic envoirnment. This document defines a mechanism via which service providers can deploy a managed layer 3 connectivity and mobility management scheme that is entirely based on the capabilities in the Network.</description>
    <dc:date>2006-09-26T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
